哈喽大家好我是王刚
Hello everyone, this is Wang Gang

本期视频为大家带来一道特色菜
In this video, I'll introduce a specialty dish

馒头炸虾球
Fried Prawn Balls with Steamed Buns

首先我们把大虾去头
First, remove the head of the prawn

从背部切开
slice open the back

去除虾线和虾壳
and peel and devein the prawns

然后加入食用盐和柠檬汁
Then add in salt and lemon juice (to the prawns)

将虾肉腌制十分钟
And marinate for 10 minutes

下一步我们准备一个白馒头
Next, grab a plain (white) steamed bun (aka mantou)

将馒头切成大小均匀的小粒备用
Cut the mantou into small evenly divided pieces, and set aside.

然后将腌制好的大虾先沾上淀粉再裹上蛋液
Coat the pre-marinated prawns with cornstarch, then with an egg wash,

最后再均匀裹上馒头粒
and finally evenly coat (the prawns) with the small mantou pieces.

再用手轻轻压紧
Use your hands to compress the coating tightly onto the prawns.

锅中油温六成热下入馒头虾
Bring the frying oil up to about 60% heat, then add in the mantou-prawns

开中小火炸五分钟
Fry them over low to medium heat for 5 minutes

将虾炸至金黄酥脆的时候倒出备用
until golden brown. Then take out the prawns and set aside.

然后锅中加入适量的蕃茄酱
and add a moderate amount of ketchup to the wok.

翻炒均匀之后加入白糖两勺
Once stir fried evenly, add in two teaspoons of white sugar

再加入少许白醋
and some white vinegar,

然后加入适量的水淀粉收紧汤汁
and add some cornstarch slurry to thicken the sauce

最后加入炸好的虾球下锅翻炒均匀即可
Finally, add in the fried prawn balls and toss evenly with the sauce.

一道非常美味的馒头炸虾球就制作完成
A very delicious dish of mantou-fried prawn balls is thus complete!

硬核家常菜
馒头炸虾球
大虾：300克
馒头一个、柠檬、鸡蛋
调料：盐、淀粉
蕃茄酱、白糖、白醋
Hardcore home-cooked dish
Mantou-Fried Prawn Balls
Large Prawns: 300g
One steamed bun (aka mantou), lemon, eggs
Seasonings: salt, cornstarch,
ketchup, white sugar, white vinegar
